Creacion de repositorios AlmaLinux 9.0
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Objetivo: Clonar los repositorios de AlmaLinux 9.0 y tenerlos locales en la LAN

1) Los repositorios que quedan configurados por defecto en une instalación básica de AlmaLinux  
   9.0 son los siguientes:

- # cat /etc/redhat-release
  AlmaLinux release 9.0 (Emerald Puma)

- # ls -l /etc/yum.repos.d/
  total 44
  -rw-r--r--. 1 root root 1019 Jul 26 18:50 almalinux-appstream.repo
  -rw-r--r--. 1 root root  983 Jul 26 18:50 almalinux-baseos.repo
  -rw-r--r--. 1 root root  947 Jul 26 18:50 almalinux-crb.repo
  -rw-r--r--. 1 root root  983 Jul 26 18:50 almalinux-extras.repo
  -rw-r--r--. 1 root root 1103 Jul 26 18:50 almalinux-highavailability.repo
  -rw-r--r--. 1 root root  947 Jul 26 18:50 almalinux-nfv.repo
  -rw-r--r--. 1 root root  959 Jul 26 18:50 almalinux-plus.repo
  -rw-r--r--. 1 root root 1103 Jul 26 18:50 almalinux-resilientstorage.repo 
  -rw-r--r--. 1 root root  935 Jul 26 18:50 almalinux-rt.repo
  -rw-r--r--. 1 root root  995 Jul 26 18:50 almalinux-saphana.repo
  -rw-r--r--. 1 root root  947 Jul 26 18:50 almalinux-sap.repo

*********************************************************************************************

2) Las URL en cada uno de los repositorios:

- # cd /etc/yum.repos.d

- # egrep '(^baseurl|# baseurl)' * | grep -v Media
  almalinux-appstream.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/almalinux/$releasever/AppStream/$basearch/os/
  almalinux-appstream.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/vault/$releasever/AppStream/debug/$basearch/
  almalinux-appstream.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/vault/$releasever/AppStream/Source/
  almalinux-baseos.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/almalinux/$releasever/BaseOS/$basearch/os/
  almalinux-baseos.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/vault/$releasever/BaseOS/debug/$basearch/
  almalinux-baseos.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/vault/$releasever/BaseOS/Source/
  almalinux-crb.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/almalinux/$releasever/CRB/$basearch/os/
  almalinux-crb.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/vault/$releasever/CRB/debug/$basearch/
  almalinux-crb.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/vault/$releasever/CRB/Source/
  almalinux-extras.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/almalinux/$releasever/extras/$basearch/os/
  almalinux-extras.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/vault/$releasever/extras/debug/$basearch/
  almalinux-extras.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/vault/$releasever/extras/Source/
  almalinux-highavailability.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/almalinux/$releasever/HighAvailability/$basearch/os/
  almalinux-highavailability.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/vault/$releasever/HighAvailability/debug/$basearch/
  almalinux-highavailability.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/vault/$releasever/HighAvailability/Source/
  almalinux-nfv.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/almalinux/$releasever/NFV/$basearch/os/
  almalinux-nfv.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/vault/$releasever/NFV/debug/$basearch/
  almalinux-nfv.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/vault/$releasever/NFV/Source/
  almalinux-plus.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/almalinux/$releasever/plus/$basearch/os/
  almalinux-plus.repo:# baseurl=https://repo.almalinux.org/vault/$releasever/plus/debug/$basearch/
